<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Location</th>
<td><span class="location"><a href="/wiki/Lebanon" title="Lebanon">Lebanon</a></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Result</th>
<td>
<ul>
<li>An estimated 130,000-250,000 people killed (some report the number much higher),</li>
<li>1,000,000 wounded half of whom were left with lifetime disability</li>
<li>billions of dollars of damage, collapse of the economy</li>
<li>complete destruction of central Beirut</li>
<li>Presence of a multitude of foreign troops, foreign occupation and invasion.</li>
<li>Israeli occupation resulted in the creation of Hezbollah.</li>
</ul>
</td>
