002 <a href="/wiki/Road_map_for_peace" title="Road map for peace">Road map for peace</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/United_Nations_Security_Council_Resolution_1559" title="United Nations Security Council Resolution 1559">2004 UNSC Resolution 1559</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/United_Nations_Security_Council_Resolution_1566" title="United Nations Security Council Resolution 1566">2004 UNSC Resolution 1566</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/United_Nations_Security_Council_Resolution_1583" title="United Nations Security Council Resolution 1583">2005 UNSC Resolution 1583</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Sharm_el-Sheikh_Summit_of_2005" title="Sharm el-Sheikh Summit of 2005">2005 Sharm el-Sheikh Summit</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;">2005 <a href="/wiki/Israel%27s_unilateral_disengagement_plan" title="Israel's unilateral disengagement plan">Israel's unilateral disengagement plan</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;">2006 <a href="/wiki/Palestinian_Prisoners%27_Document" title="Palestinian Prisoners' Document">Palestinian Prisoners' Document</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/United_Nations_Security_Council_Resolution_1701" title="United Nations Security Council Resolution 1701">2006 UNSC Resolution 1701</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;">2007 <a href="/wiki/Annapolis_Conference" title="Annapolis Conference">Annapolis Conference</a></span></div>
